3. Implemented dynamic product display with variants
4. Added cart functionality
5. Included proper meta fields and schema
6. Added responsive design elements
7. Implemented wishlist functionality
8. Added product reviews section
9. Included related products section
10. Added proper navigation using Shopify linklists

